name: Teamo.ru
overview:
Teamo.ru is a fast growing Russian online dating website helping to match single Russian speaking adults throughout the world, of any age or religion, looking for a serious relationship.

The service uses complex scientific algorithms to match singles once they have undertaken a personality test and updated their personal profile, helping to make sure users are only linked to those who best match their characteristics. The test has been developed by leading Russian psychologists and approved by “The British Psychology Society”.

Teamo.ru allows users to learn as much as they can about other singles in the shortest time possible. They can browse through their list of matches and decide who they would like to contact. Teamo.ru currently has a database near 1M registered users and is constantly growing.

Teamo.ru was established by a team with extensive expertise in the Russian internet. The company was initially funded by Fast Lane Ventures.

The company’s investment partner is UMJ Russia Fund, the venture fund managed by United Managers Japan, Inc. (Japan). Taking into account its original investment, the total investment amount into Teamo.ru now stands at more than 2 million US dollars.

For more information, please visit www.teamo.ru

funding_rounds.source_description: Teamo.ru Raises Funding from UMJ Russia Fund
